Package org.eclipse.emf.compare

Interface ResourceAttachmentChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Diff, EObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResourceAttachmentChangeImpl, ResourceAttachmentChangeSpec
    public interface ResourceAttachmentChange
extends Diff
    A representation of the model object 'Resource Attachment Change'. This particular kind of difference describes the fragmentation (or un-fragmentation) of a model element in its own (or back in its parent's) resource.

    The following features are supported:

    • Resource URI
